==== Natalam ====

Natalam, Kristi bhavartiank Kristachea dusrea yenneak toyar korta.  Hem Kristachem dusrem yennem fuddarak ek khori ghoddnni.  Ti kenna ghoddttoli hem ami nook.  Tea khatir ami amchea patkantlim utthun Krista vatten vollunk goroz.  Patok Devachea Rajeachea yenneak addkholl zaunk favonam.  Zuanv Batista bhaxen Povitr Sobha, Kristavank sogllo vell monstap (repentance) porgott korta ani Somiachea hea dusrea yenneak toyar asunk ulo marta. 

Sumar chovtea xekddeant thavn Kristanvam Jezucho zolm (Natalam) somarombhunk laglim.  Natalam ho ek chodd umedicho sonn.  Zoxem zoxem hi porob lagim pavot ieta toxem-toxem ek attvich umed ani anon dattun yeta.  Khuxalkai bhoron yeta.  

Natalanchi porob Goychea vatavoronnant Goykarank ek soglleant vhodd ani anondbhorit porob.  Somest Goykarank ektthaim haddpi hi porob. He porbe nimitan soirim-dairim, ixtt-mitram ekamekak mellttat, vicharpus kortat. Kitlei motbhed,vaittponn aslear legit, Natalanchea disa sogllim ektthaim zatat.  Pordesant ani aispos aslolim Goykaram Natalank aplea ganv-ghora yevpacho nem dhortat.  Aplea kuttumba vangdda hi porob korunk anvddetat. Natalam khorench ek kuttumbik porob.

Aiz Natalam ek jagtik (global) somarombh zala.  He porbe vixim poramporo dosturio (customs) ani jevnnam-khannam zori desam, sonskrutayam ani hovamana pormannem veg-vegllim tori tea disachi umed sogllim ontoram hupta.  Ho porbecho dis soglleank suttiecho dis zallean hi porob konnachoi somaromb koso zala.  Je bhaxen aiz him Natalam zatat te drixttin hie porbent sonvsari ani udeogi mon dhirim-dhirim bhitor sorunk laglam. 

Pun khorea Natalanchie porbecho orth Biblient melltta. Xubvortomanachea don pustokancher tacho ullekh asa : Matev 1: 18-25 ani Lukas 2 : 1-20.  konn bhaxen Mariek Jezu zolmolo tem hea avesvoramni sanglam.  Tachea zolma vixim jeo vichitr vostu ghoddleo teo Devachie yevzonne pormannim zaleo oxem Kristanvam sotmantat.  Jezu ek khalto ani durboll monis-rupan ailo.  Provadianchea pustokamni tachea zolmachi khobor adim guddench sangloli asli. 

