== Survatechim utram ==
Natal Kristanvanchi dusri vhodd porôb, Paskam uprant.

Jezu Kristacho zolmacho dis konnech thiraien sangunk zaina, punn hinvachea vô xi'iechea disamnim zala mhunn somoz asa.

== Jezu Kristacho Zolom' ==
Jezu Kristacho zolom' Belea nogra zalo. Devan bhasail'lo sonvsaracho soddvondar-acho vô Tarôk-acho zolom' eka gorvam-gottheant zalo. Tachi avôi Ankvar Maria, ji Povitr Otmeachea kurpent gorbest zali. Ankvar Morien, San Juzek lognnache utor dilelem.

Agust Romi patxai-achea razvottke vellar, Kirin razpalan aplea rajeant, lok kitlo aslo tem mezunk, hukum' ghatlo. Dor dadlean ap-aplea ganvant vochun nond korpachi goroz aslelean, San Juze Galileiachea Nazaret ganvasun Belea nogra gelo.

=== Jezuchea Zolmak Boddve, Menddream-Rakhnne ani Rai ===
Oso adlo somoz asa ki, Anj-Boddveanim Ankvar Moriek zolom' ditanam adar dilo. Boddveanim ''Gloria in excelsis Deo'' gaion ontrollar gailem ani Devak vakhannlo.

Jezuk polleunk gorvam rakhnne aile. Udentiche tin rai Melkior, Gaspar ani Bartolomeu eka nokhetrak polleun aile. Tannim bhangar, gondh-ros bi haddlim.

=== Herod Jezuk marunk sodta ===
Jezuk bhett korpachea adim udentiche tin rai Raza Herod-ak mellunk ailole. Raza Herod-ak Jezuchea zolmachi khobor koll'li. Herod-ik ballkak marunk zai aslo kiteak Jezu raza aslo. Jezuk nomoskar korunk udentichea tin rai-ank fott marun, Tacho zolmacho zago kollounk lailem. Punn Jezuk bhett korun, udentichea tin raiank eka sopnnam vorvim, Devan tankam aplea desak veglli vatt dhorunk laili. 

Herodik hem koll'lea uprant, soglleam don vorsam unnem aslolea putank marpak hukum' ghatlo.

